results.title: Funny pigeon painting, Live Love Poop pigeon print, funny pigeon drawing, Live Love Laugh print, cute bird art, bird decor - 5x7" matted art
results.description:
LIVE LOVE POOP. I love pigeons, especially working-class city pigeons. They are so resilient, smart and loyal. It always makes me a little bit sad when I see them plodding along a dirty city street. They seem so baffled yet persistent, just going about their business on the ground as if they've forgotten that they can fly.

So, instead of the overused, eyeroll-inducing LIVE LOVE LAUGH sign, this is my version of an inspirational life motto.

This print would obviously be great hanging in a guest bathroom, or as a gift to the co-worker who spends an inordinately long time in the bathroom.

All pre-matted prints are ready to drop into a 5x7" frame. I've carefully selected different mat colors to complement the artwork itself, and you have your choice of options from the drop-down menu. These little prints make great gifts because they are very easy to frame!

This cute print arrives with a colorful mat, chipboard backing, and packed in a cellophane sleeve. 

This is an archival print of my original artwork, which was done in marker and watercolor.

The artwork is packed in a cardboard mailer to protect it during shipping.

results.title: Folded Book Pattern for a Rose Silhouette - 549 pages 18 cm centered
results.description:
This is a cut and fold pattern for a silhouette of a rose. 

The sample was done with a 180 fold, which is recommended but not necessary.  YouTube has some videos on how to do a 180 fold but it's basically simply folding in each page 1-2 cm then using this new edge as the edge of the book.

This makes a great addition to any home decor or a gift for a loved one.

All of our patterns are tested.

You will need a book with at least 549 pages and where the pages are at least 18cm high. 



Although I am in the USA... I find it a lot more precise and easy to use centimeters so this pattern is in cm.  


This is for the pattern only, not on how to do a MMCF (Measure, Mark, Cut, Fold).   If you need direction on 'how to' there are many youtube videos.
  

Note that this is a digital file.  That means when you purchase, you will immediately have access to the file.  Because of this, we are unable to offer any refunds.  If you have any questions please ask.
